item.title: How do i log on to another server?Someone Plz Help
item.dc:creator: @MMcgrady1 MMcgrady1
item.description:
@MMcgrady1 wrote:

  1. Open up your MoparScape client.
  2. Wait for it to load up.
  3. Look for a “file” tab located at the top left hand corner, click on it then click “New Server”
  4. Enter the server’s IP and if you have to change the port click on file then “New Port”.
  5. Enter in any name and password then click login.
    *6. If its hamachi, download it.
    *7. Join the network.
    *8. Do the same thing as you did for a no-ip server and you should be playing

*- Hamachi servers, if you want to play them, follow steps 6-8.

To download hamachi go to this url
http://www.hamachi.cc/download/list.php
click on the first big blue button.
